data.description: 2% toward the buyers' closing cost. This custom-built, ranch-style, secluded, brick home is a MUST-SEE!!! This beautifully renovated home has so much to offer. High-quality LVP flooring throughout the main living areas, eucalyptus hardwood flooring in the primary bedroom, ceramic tile in the bathrooms, laundry room, and flex room, and carpet flooring in the remaining bedrooms. There is an in-law suite with a separate entrance and access from the house, which offers a large living room, a bedroom, and a full bathroom. Chef's kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and soft-close cabinets. The large living room has a wood-burning brick fireplace, large windows, and a skylight. Access to the covered back porch or huge sun deck through the living room. The other features include a massive laundry room, office space, breakfast/flex room, and a huge 3500 sf unfinished basement with a brick fireplace. The roof was replaced in 2014, and the HVAC was replaced in 2016.
